OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,FGuernsey's Elizabeth College has
OL,7,Frejected allegations made by former
OL,8,Fpupils in a national newspaper that it
OL,9,Frepeatedly dismissed claims of
OL,10,Fhistorical sexual and physical abuse.
OL,12,FIt comes after the school announced an
OL,13,Fexternal investigation last week into
OL,14,Faccusations of historical child abuse,
OL,15,Fsaying it had received "a number of
OL,16,Fdisclosures" in recent months of
OL,17,F"alleged non-recent abuse concerning
OL,18,Fthe experiences of former pupils in
OL,19,Fthe 1970s and 1980s".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
