PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,FHowever, three ex-students have told
OL,7,Fthe Observer that they repeatedly
OL,8,Fraised concerns with the College at
OL,9,Fthe time and in the years since, which
OL,10,Fwere disregarded.
OL,12,FIn response, an Elizabeth College
OL,13,Fspokesperson says: "The College
OL,14,Fstrongly disputes claims reported in
OL,15,Fthe Observer that it repeatedly
OL,16,Fdismissed victims' concerns.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,F"Any disclosures received from former
OL,7,Fpupils were treated with the utmost
OL,8,Fseriousness, followed up by the
OL,9,FCollege, and reports made to the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,F"The College is unequivocal in its
OL,13,Fcondemnation of any form of abuse, and
OL,14,Fdeeply regrets and apologises to
OL,15,Fanyone who has suffered abuse at the
OL,16,FCollege."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
