CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,FGuernsey's most senior Anglican priest
OL,7,Fwho sits on the College's Governance
OL,8,Fboard, The Very Reverend Tim Barker,
OL,9,Fhas also apologised after the Observer
OL,10,Freported an internal email he wrote in
OL,11,Fresponse to a former pupil's claim of
OL,12,Fphysical abuse.
OL,14,FThe newspaper says the Very Reverend
OL,15,FBarker stated: "Any sort of
OL,16,Finvestigation that we might attempt
OL,17,Fwould inevitably be flawed and would
OL,18,Fbe a distraction from other priorities
OL,19,F(although I do not think that the last
OL,20,Fcomment should be disclosed to the
OL,21,Fcomplainant)."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,FIn response, the priest told ITV News:
OL,7,F"I deeply regret that the language
OL,8,Fused in discussing the question of
OL,9,Ffurther attempts at investigation by
OL,10,Fthe College itself, when taken out of
OL,11,Fcontext, appeared insensitive.
OL,13,F"That was never my intention. I offer
OL,14,Fthe complainant an unqualified apology.
OL,16,F"Further disclosures concerning the
OL,17,Fcomplainant's experiences and those of
OL,18,Fothers led the Board to commission
OL,19,Fthis review by an independent expert,
OL,20,Fa decision I fully endorse."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
