PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Elizabeth College
OL,7,Fadds: "The paucity of College records
OL,8,Ffrom the time, the fact that the key
OL,9,Falleged perpetrator was no longer
OL,10,Falive, together with the lack of any
OL,11,Fother known disclosures concerning
OL,12,Fthem, made it difficult to establish
OL,13,Fany facts around these matters.
OL,15,F"The College nonetheless took their
OL,16,Fdisclosures seriously and encouraged
OL,17,Fthe former pupil to report their
OL,18,Fconcerns to the police and encourage
OL,19,Fany other survivors of whom they were
OL,20,Faware to do the same.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
