CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776885106
OL,3,CSchool rejects allegations of child
OL,4,Cabuse cover-up from former pupils
OL,6,F"It was never the intention of the
OL,7,FCollege or Tim Barker to cover up or
OL,8,Fdiminish the seriousness of the
OL,9,Fcomplainant's disclosures."
OL,11,FElizabeth College was founded by Royal
OL,12,FCharter under Queen Elizabeth I in
OL,13,F1563, and costs between #15,297 and
OL,14,F#16,995 per year to attend.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
